","body":"난 그냥 내버려 둬도 돼!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"band2-005-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"토모 찡도 말했지만~ \n이런 서류를 보니 역시 기쁘다앙~\n본격적이라고 해야 하나~ 에헤헤 그치? 란~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"band2-005-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"란","body":"……뭐, 그렇지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"band2-005-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"출연도 정해졌고\n오늘부터는 본격적으로 빡세게 연습해야겠어.\n그러면 빨리……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"band2-005-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"히마리","body":"우후후~!\n얘들아 연습 전에 보여주고 싶은 게 있어!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"moti